column2: SELECT SUM(TIV_2016) AS TIV_2016 FROM (SELECT PID, TIV_2015, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY TIV_2015) AS CT_2015, TIV_2016, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY (CAST(LAT AS VARCHAR) || CAST(LON AS VARCHAR))) AS CT_LOCATION FROM INSURANCE) AS SUB WHERE CT_2015 > 1 AND CT_LOCATION = 1

SELECT SUM(tiv_2016) AS tiv_2016 FROM (SELECT tiv_2016, COUNT(tiv_2015) OVER (PARTITION BY tiv_2015) AS dr1, COUNT(tiv_2015) OVER (PARTITION BY lat, lon) AS dr2 FROM insurance) AS t WHERE dr1 >= 2 AND dr2 = 1

SELECT SUM(TIV_2016) AS TIV_2016 FROM (SELECT TIV_2015, TIV_2016, LAT, LON, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY TIV_2015) AS CNT_TIV_2015, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY LAT, LON) AS CNT_LAT_LON FROM INSURANCE) AS SUB WHERE CNT_TIV_2015 > 1 AND CNT_LAT_LON = 1
